{"article_id":"zrIhVbSVa8UNTOsE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Now that Donald Trump Jr. has admitted to having had a meeting with a Kremlin-connected Russian lawyer during the presidential campaign","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"because she promised him negative information on Hillary Clinton ,","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"it ' s time","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"to revisit all the times","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Trump and his advisers denied any such contacts .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The Washington Post helpfully rounds up seven such denials , three of them from Trump Jr. himself .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"One of Uday ' s denials , of course , was on Saturday ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"when he was asked about his meeting with Natalia Veselnitskaya","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and claimed","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that \" We primarily discussed a program about the adoption of Russian children. \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"But in March , he said","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"that during the campaign , \" Did I meet with people","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that were Russian ?","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"I ' m sure ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"I ' m sure","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"I did \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"but \" certainly none","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that I was representing the campaign in any way , shape or form. \"","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"And in July 2016 , not long after his meeting with Veselnitskaya ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"asked about the Clinton campaign ' s allegations","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that Russia was trying to help Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Junior said","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that \" I ca n't think of bigger lies ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"but that exactly goes to show you what the DNC and what the Clinton camp will do .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"They will lie","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"and do anything","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"to win . \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Trump the Father denied collusion , too , in January ,","depth":3},{"id":28,"text":"though only off camera","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"and after making himself look guilty","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"by ducking the question","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"when it was asked during a press conference .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"But ,","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"after ducking that public question twice","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"- \" Can you stand here today , once and for all ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and say","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that no one","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"connected to you or your campaign","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"had any contact with Russia","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"leading up to or during the presidential campaign ? \" -","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"two reporters said","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"that later , off camera , Trump gave a firm denial .","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"Mike Pence went with \" of course not \" in response to two different versions of the collusion question .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Kellyanne Conway said","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"\" absolutely not. \"","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Sean Spicer referred reporters back to Donald Trump ' s off-camera denial .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"And they all said all of those things","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"after Donald Jr. met with a Russian with Kremlin ties","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"who said","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"she had damaging information on Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Lies , lies , and also lies .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":101,"left":77,"right":100,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":55,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":52,"right":54,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":52,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":2,"right":53,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"el